Module kivakit.core.kernel
Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.kernel.messaging.messages

Class Result<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.telenav.kivakit.core.kernel.messaging.messages.Result<T>
  • public class Result<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    A return value that contains an object OR a Message indicating that something went wrong. Success messages should not be returned with this object as the failed() method only tests for the existence of any message.
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
